reviews.text:
Stop it right now...

This place is the cutest! My wife and I decided to stop in on the 4th of July to hang out on their patio and try some of their vegan...
I can't say enough kind words about Woodhouse Vegan. They have an excellent selection of vegan foods that even the picky or discerning carnivore could enjoy...

Sadly I did not take pictures to record all the delicious food my party had, but I'm here to tell you everything was amazing.
